metadata.name: WAGMI [1 of 1]
metadata.description:
WAGMI by b 
1 out of 1
12 seconds minted in 4k
Liquid masking over "WAGMI" by BLCK

BLCK is a Creator | Collector
more known as the guy behind TABYBL 
"The Agency BY Black Label"
B comes from a marketing background and has been running the powerhouse of digital marketing for multiple years in Asia, telling stories for brands.

Every project that The Agency takes on, is garnished with artistic while minimalistic elements, making every detail matter, as the love of art is a necessity. 

Be part of the movement, 
everyone starts somewhere, and B's NFT journey starts here. 

Music custom made by Milam Music.
His tracks have been premiered on SWEET MUSIQUE, HYPEBEAST and has been featured on the front page of APPLE MUSIC CHINA.

Connect with B by owning it.
